Dear Lover of Romance:
 
The beauty of unexpected passion is that it takes you by surprise. But the
danger of unexpected passion is that it...well, you can guess that one,
can't you? If not, just ask Mona Graham or David Anderson or Julie Carlson
what happens when love arrives unexpectedly.
 
*   *   *
Mona Graham is a mystic on a quest for an ancient treasure. Patrick Maxwell
is a rogue knight who's a sworn enemy to her family. She chooses him to
accompany her on a fateful journey, with the promise of peace at last
between their two clans. That is, if the two of them survive the
journey...and their own desire. Medieval romance lights up the Dark Ages in
Jen Holling's CAPTURED BY YOUR KISS!
 
