4. Five winners will be selected at random from among all eligible entries
received in a drawing to be held on or about January 23, 2003. The winners
will be notified by email. Sponsor is not responsible, and may disqualify a
potential winner if the corresponding email address does not work or it is
changed without timely prior notice to Simon & Schuster via email at
SSOnline@SimonSays.com <mailto:SSOnline@SimonSays.com> . Odds of winning
depend on the number of eligible entries received. 
 
 
